name: Slick-white
body:
#### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
Slick White a really really simple BetterDiscord theme. I am no master coder or master-crafter, not even a master discord user. I woke up and decided that hey lets give it a go and i hope people enjoy it as much as i did when i spent time working on it

### Authors and Contributors
Yurgburg that is I for now.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble contact me on discord @YurgBurg#6184. (until I can make another email)
